As part of our commitment to supporting young talents, #DolceGabbana and @istitutomarangoni_milano organized a series of workshops with students to share ideas and reinterpret the most treasured values of Dolce&Gabbana.

The best talents are going to start a learning journey as part of the Dolce&Gabbana Design department to explore their visions and interpretation of fashion.

Introducing Dolce&Gabbana x P.J. Tucker, the Special Collection created in collaboration with @pjtucker.
 
The American basketball player’s aesthetic combined with #DolceGabbana’s creativity have given life to two new interpretations of the Miami sneaker, inspired by basketball sneakers from the early 90s. 
 
The 100 pairs of the sneakers, signed by P. J. Tucker, are paired to an exclusive NFT - the acronym for Non-Fungible Token - digital authenticity certificate. 
 
Shop the online preview, available exclusively at the link in bio.

node.text:
Exploring our roots to create what's next: introducing #DGNextChapter, the Women's Fall Winter 21 Fashion Show.
 
In collaboration with @istitutoitalianoditecnologia, the #DGFW21 Collection reveals how technology and craftsmanship, two apparently different worlds, come together in a celebration of Fatto a Mano. The new looks, inspired by robotics research and Artificial Intelligence, also pay tribute to #DolceGabbana DNA of the ‘90s. 
 
Stay tuned for the Fashion Show on Monday, March 1st at 4PM CET.

The latest twist on the iconic #DolceGabbana DNA, inspired by the bright, vibrant colours of the Sicilian Cart print, comes together for an endless summer vibe. 
 
Discover the #DGCarretto collection with sizes available up to an Italian 54 at the link in bio. 
 
#MadeInItaly
